WEBVTT

00:09:58.208 --> 00:10:02.101
we are so much more capable
of solving problems,

00:10:02.125 --> 00:10:04.976
being creative, being adaptive,

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:06.851
being flexible,

00:10:06.875 --> 00:10:09.083
being our brilliant selves, right?

00:10:10.708 --> 00:10:13.934
So what if our climate
and environmental work

00:10:13.958 --> 00:10:16.476
was informed by these concepts, right,

00:10:16.500 --> 00:10:19.268
of window of tolerance,

00:10:19.292 --> 00:10:21.268
lot of double binds

00:10:21.292 --> 00:10:22.958
and attunement?

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:26.184
So it can look like a whole lot of things.

00:10:26.208 --> 00:10:27.476
So I'm asked all the time,

00:10:27.500 --> 00:10:31.059
"OK, Renee, this sounds awesome
for a clinical context,